                              <Assign.Value>
                                <InArgument x:TypeArguments="x:String" xml:space="preserve">Summary:

1. General Medical Condition:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Acute exacerbation of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)
Hypertension
2. Surgical Case:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Acute appendicitis with suspected perforation
Abdominal pain and fever
3. Cardiac Case:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Acute myocardial infarction (ST-elevation)
Unstable angina
4. Neurological Condition:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Acute ischemic stroke, left middle cerebral artery (MCA) distribution
Right-sided weakness and slurred speech
5. Respiratory Condition:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Pneumonia, community-acquired, right lower lobe
Shortness of breath and cough with sputum production
6. Infectious Disease:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Urinary tract infection with sepsis
Fever, dysuria, and altered mental status
7. Trauma:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Closed head injury, Glasgow Coma Scale 14
Contusion to the left forehead following a fall
8. Obstetric:
Admitting Diagnosis:

Preterm labor at 32 weeks gestation
Abdominal cramping and cervical dilation</InArgument>
